        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nI am a bit confused about the versioning mechanism.\nSomeone created 1.2.1 version and Arul changed the version to 1.2.2-SNAPSHOT.\nSo, 1.2.1 release is exactly the same as 1.2.0.\n\nI would have expected that the version would remain 1.2.1-SNAPSHOT until Arul's change is pushed and that we decide to make his changes the 1.2.1 release (and then prepare for the next patch by changing the version to 1.2.2-SNAPSHOT)",
